headline.print_headline: Mostly Abandoned Kansas City Building Collapses
headline.main: Mostly Abandoned Kansas City Building Collapses

lead_paragraph: A vehicle being chased by police slammed into a downtown Kansas City building where vintage cars were being stored Thursday, causing the structure to partially collapse and sending at least one vehicle plummeting to the ground from the second floor.
